		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Update: the server did <strong>not</strong> crash - Morv powercycled the router and it grabbed a new IP address, and FreeBSD got confused; not knowing how to reset DHCP, he rebooted the server.
<br />
<br />He now knows the proper method to reset DHCP (dhclient -r; dhclient xl0), so this hopefully shouldn't happen again.

		

		</td>
