<br />Removing one DIMM seemed to make the errors go away, but Morv wasn't able to test the "bad" DIMM before leaving for work; he likely tested it about an hour ago (during which a "The System is Down" page was visible), but I won't know the results until I get home from work (in about 5 and a half hours).

		

